  "original_title": "\u0b92\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0bb5\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0baa\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0bae\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd 3 \u0b86\u0bb5\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0b95\u0bc2\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bca\u0b9f\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b86\u0b95\u0bb8\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bcd 3 \u0b87\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b86\u0bb0\u0bae\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The 3rd Session of the Ninth Parliament begins on 3 August",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "The third session of the Ninth Parliament will be inaugurated by President Ranil Wickramawasinghe on the 3rd of August. The 2nd session was adjourned on 28th midnight.",
        "President Ranil Wickremesinghe issued a special gazette announcement on the 28th regarding the completion of the 2nd session and the commencement of the 3rd session.",
        "The 2nd session of Parliament was adjourned with effect from midnight on the 28th in accordance with Article 70 of the Constitution.",
        "The 3rd session of the Parliament will be formally opened on the 3rd of the next month with a special speech by the President.",
        "Following the adjournment of the parliamentary session, the parliamentary committees including the COP committee, the COP committee and the finance committee will be dissolved as usual and new committees will be appointed."
      ],
